Privacy Policy
1. Purpose of Personal Information Collection and Use
This app collects minimal personal information necessary for managing and improving users' exercise records.
2. Types of Personal Information Collected
Basic personal identification information (e.g., name, email address)
Exercise record data (e.g., type of exercise, duration, calories burned)
3. Retention and Use Period of Personal Information
Personal information is retained until the user deletes their account or withdraws from the app.
4. Procedure and Method for Destruction of Personal Information
Personal information is promptly destroyed once the purpose of its collection is achieved.
5. Provision and Sharing of Personal Information
Personal information is not provided to third parties except in cases of legal requirements or with user consent.
